		<h2>Puget Sound Outdoors</h2>

		The campus outdoor program, Puget Sound Outdoors, constantly offers weekend trips all through Washington. Among the most popular outings include skiing, rock-climbing, whitewater kayaking, and leadership training on the Washington coast. Additionally, UPS hosts a Wilderness First Aid course on campus semiannually. <a href = "http://www.pugetsound.edu/student-life/student-activities/puget-sound-outdoors/">Click here</a> to find out more about PSO and their trips throughout Washington.
